  <brief_title>Citrulline in Severe Sepsis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective, Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled Phase II Trial of Intravenous Citrulline to Prevent or Mitigate Acute Lung Injury in Patients With Severe Sepsis</official_title>
